cheetah finds the base and cheetah and tigerhawk enter the base.
 Nic <wingedwarrior41@...> wrote:OOC: Thanks for adopting a more cheerful signature, Tankor.

BIC:

Tyrael stepped in the doorway and answered his two soldiers.

Tyrael: It's not that far. Keep looking, you'll find it.

He proceeds inside and looks around. This was indeed a top of the art 
warship. He went in the direction where he thought the bridge was.

As he came in a vast room, he stood at attention.

Tyrael: Major Tyrael of the Tripredacus Strikers Unit reporting, sir!
